    <item>
      <title>Version 0.2.4</title>
      <link>https://jkawamoto.github.io/roadie/release/v0.2.4/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Sep 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://jkawamoto.github.io/roadie/release/v0.2.4/</guid>
      <description>

&lt;h3 id=&#34;added&#34;&gt;Added&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support a new URL scheme &lt;code&gt;roadie://&lt;/code&gt; which is a shortcut to
&lt;code&gt;gs://&amp;lt;your bucket&amp;gt;/.roadie/&amp;lt;section&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; in script files.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example, a URL &lt;code&gt;roadie://sample.dat&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;data&lt;/code&gt; section of your script file,
will be treated as &lt;code&gt;gs://&amp;lt;your bucket&amp;gt;/.roadie/data/sample.dat&lt;/code&gt;.
It will reduce your types to make script files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/jkawamoto/roadie/releases/v0.2.4&#34;&gt;Download&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
