      <description>

&lt;h3 id=&#34;added&#34;&gt;Added&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support &lt;code&gt;--retry&lt;/code&gt; option by default it is set to 10.&lt;/li&gt;
